10 REM SMOKE: PROGRAM AREA HOLDS LOTS OF POKE LINES
20 REM 200 POKE LINES SHOULD FIT EASILY IN PS=16384 TOKEN AREA.
30 REM IF THIS FAILS WE NEED FR-2 (DATA/READ) TO COMPRESS IMAGES.
40 LET S=0
50 FOR I=0 TO 199
60 POKE I,I
70 NEXT I
80 FOR I=0 TO 199
90 LET S=S+PEEK(I)
100 NEXT I
110 PRINT "SUM ";S
120 REM EXPECT: 19900 (= 199*200/2)
130 END
RUN
BYE
